  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd 9 \u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0bc2\u0baa\u0bbe \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd 3 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "3 people arrested with gold worth 9 million rupees in Mannar Pechala beach",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "About 470 grams of gold and conch (Valampuri) which were tried to be smuggled out of the country during a special operation carried out by the navy last night (25) in Mannar Baysala sea area have been seized.",
        "The Navy carried out special patrolling operations in the Besalai-Thalimannar sea area last Monday night.",
        "During this, the marines inspected a boat that had traveled suspiciously from the Besalai beach.",
        "The navy seized 470 grams of gold and Valampuri conch from the said boat.",
        "The navy has arrested 3 suspects involved in the incident and the dinghy used to smuggle the goods.",
        "Meanwhile, the market value of gold seized in this operation is Rs. 09 million said by the navy.",
        "The suspects arrested by the Navy have been identified as belonging to Puttalam and Besalai areas between the ages of 24 and 39, the Navy said.",
        "The suspects along with the gold, conches and boats have been handed over by the Navy to the Customs office in Jaffna for further legal action."
      ],
